    schema:name "Fix 2 remaining GitHub fabricated IRIs in ACME Sales section (lines 582, 594)"@en ;
    schema:description "Two entity hrefs in the ACME Sales Knowledge Bundle section (line 582: okf:KnowledgeBundle; line 594: okf:isForeignKeyTo) still pointed to GitHub repository URLs after the earlier 7-fix pass. Canonical DAV IRI base confirmed from SPARQL accordion PREFIX declarations: https://linkeddata.uriburner.com/DAV/demos/daas/okf-open-knowledge-format-ontology.ttl. Both entities verified in local ontology TTL (okf-ontology-claude_sonnet_4_6-1.ttl): KnowledgeBundle at line 47, isForeignKeyTo at line 204. Post-fix grep on 'github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform' returned zero results — all fabricated GitHub IRIs eliminated."@en ;
    schema:object <../../../../../LLMs/Claude%20Generated/webpages/okf-infographic-claude_sonnet_4_6-1.html> ;
    schema:result "2 edits applied. Zero GitHub IRIs remain anywhere in the HTML file."@en .

