    schema:name "Hyperlink all 7 glossary definition divs in okf-infographic-claude_sonnet_4_6-1.html"@en ;
    schema:description "All 7 <div class='def'> definition texts were plain text with no hyperlinks — a direct violation of rdf-infographic-skill contract line 1135 and CLAUDE.md entity hyperlink contract. Wrapped each def text in <a href='resolver?url=...#TermXxx' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'> using the same IRI already used for the sibling term name link. Terms fixed: TermKnowledgeBundle, TermEnrichmentAgent, TermKnowledgeConsumer, TermLLMWikiPattern, TermYAMLFrontmatter, TermProducerConsumerIndependence, TermFormatNotPlatform. Also updated section comment from 'Section 10' to 'Section 11' to reflect renumbering after HowTo insertion."@en ;
